      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "XENTARO (2) narrowly missed out on the hat-trick last start when beaten in a photo finish here a fortnight ago. He maps to get every chance again today for Chris Parnham and the form out of his last start has already been franked. Can bounce back to winning ways now. NONESOSPICY (6) is building nicely, finishing 0.7L off the winner fresh before a 0.5L defeat most recently over 1200m here. Back to 1000m looks ideal and Pike is unbeaten when riding the mare. She can sit up front coming back to 1000m and another forward showing is on the cards. LORD SHIVA (1) comes through the same race as XENTARO last start where he jumped the equal favourite. He sat up front there and was gunned down late. Nottle rides now with her 2kg claim coming in handy and he can make his presence felt. LAST STYLEBENDER (5) is looking for the hat-trick and can't be discounted. BONNIE LAD (7) is worth including on the fresh effort.",
